sequenceDiagram
    actor Agent as AI Agent
    participant Coord as MemoryCoordinator
    participant Mgr as MemoryManager
    participant DB as MemoryDatabase
    participant SQLite as SQLite file
    participant TreeCLI as amplihack memory tree
    participant CleanCLI as amplihack memory clean
    participant TransferCLI as amplihack memory export/import
    participant Archive as JSON/Kuzu archive

    Agent->>Coord: store_memory(session_id, content, type)
    Coord->>Mgr: create_entry(MemoryEntry)
    Mgr->>DB: store(entry)
    DB->>SQLite: INSERT INTO memories(...)
    SQLite-->>DB: ok
    DB-->>Mgr: stored entry
    Mgr-->>Coord: success

    Note over Agent,SQLite: Stored session memory is SQLite-backed

    Agent->>Coord: retrieve_memories(query)
    Coord->>Mgr: search(MemoryQuery)
    Mgr->>DB: retrieve(query)
    DB->>SQLite: SELECT ... WHERE ...
    SQLite-->>DB: rows
    DB-->>Mgr: list[MemoryEntry]
    Mgr-->>Coord: results

    Note over TreeCLI,Archive: User can inspect, clean, or transfer memory

    actor User
    User->>TreeCLI: amplihack memory tree --backend sqlite --session abc
    TreeCLI->>DB: retrieve(session_id=abc)
    DB->>SQLite: SELECT ...
    SQLite-->>DB: rows
    DB-->>TreeCLI: entries
    TreeCLI-->>User: tree visualization

    User->>CleanCLI: amplihack memory clean --backend sqlite --pattern test_*
    CleanCLI->>DB: list_sessions()
    DB->>SQLite: SELECT sessions
    SQLite-->>DB: matching rows
    CleanCLI->>DB: delete_session(match)
    DB->>SQLite: DELETE FROM sessions
    SQLite-->>DB: deleted rows
    CleanCLI-->>User: cleanup summary

    User->>TransferCLI: amplihack memory export/import
    TransferCLI->>Archive: read/write portable memory bundle
    Archive-->>TransferCLI: JSON or Kuzu payload
    TransferCLI-->>User: transfer result
